{"tid":1241680,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲: 白官聯署 PLEASE LIBERATE HONG KONG","createTime":"2019-06-18T19:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T04:08:45.000Z","uid":28257,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a07ce149cfcfcf2b46aad3b1dec941d134fdc581","tid":1241680,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:43:20.000Z","msg":"我地99.99的人同素未謀面梁凌杰，我地甚至佢個樣貌係點都唔知。呢三日佢打動左我地幾多人的心靈，或多或少左右了香港的命運。<br />\n<br />\n況且陳雲，一個人如果唔愛香港，唔會日復如日，年復如年咁下筆，個到係多少的精力。佢盡佢前半一生，保護嶺南/香港文化，下半生，於政治路途上啟蒙港人。 <br />\n<br />\n一個人一個群眾如果冇失去左文化同語言，就會失去其身分，各人登山各自努力，陳雲佢何嘗唔係盡自己之所能，以一人之力保衛香港。<br />\n<br />\n有印象都知佢痛恨左膠，從不休其筆伐口誅，呢刻竟然整白官聯署，必有其意思，希望大家可以幫助聯署。上次大家用行動否定左佢，今次可否用行動支持佢一次? <br />\n<br />\n有時，有D野係總要出師有名<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR3j8Mc3iHSx7X7wemMa8ZPXXu_Gs-43LHB4qVViBMUZf5yzwEj9WFYDtu0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3j8Mc3iHSx7X7wemMa8ZPXXu_Gs-43LHB4qVViBMUZf5yzwEj9WFYDtu0&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8Ay7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=3c2b678b\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR3j8Mc3iHSx7X7wemMa8ZPXXu_Gs-43LHB4qVViBMUZf5yzwEj9WFYDtu0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，大家警惕，好好保護自己 為自己做好後授工作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CWpaEtx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCWpaEtx.png&h=7e7b43d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jDiOmS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jDiOmS.jpg&h=cb0ca6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZyJF1GT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZyJF1GT.png&h=e8792d65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e8d1caad8988449e291b6b19d9319e772dae78e","tid":1241680,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:47:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5b04856d84ae43774c2ed23cf96cfd6e79d0346","tid":1241680,"uid":254729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:52:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3796cdab8c3784f93ab3c3a3814a7266f22917bd","tid":1241680,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T20:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f4bd223b57aa36007561de8b26e7bc78598b05","tid":1241680,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T20:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31a9769254537127c9af99f78944ab63b9f9ed6","tid":1241680,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T22:52:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07de962a38b97c0f088c7afea7675b568a78e589","tid":1241680,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T22:53:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d0e6230ff39cadef8e2d28e4edafdad72526b05c","tid":1241680,"uid":132478,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:01:07.000Z","msg":"唔好嚮烈士全朵啦"},{"pid":"8585d847892d9d2b86372957abb25335bceb0092","tid":1241680,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0e6230ff39cadef8e2d28e4edafdad72526b05c","tid":1241680,"uid":132478,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:01:07.000Z","msg":"唔好嚮烈士全朵啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:17:20.000Z","msg":"我唔知邊個發起呢樣野，點解唔應該講烈士個名?佢又唔係佛地魔? <br />\n<br />\n唔係應該，當要輕藐某人個陣，先唔用佢的名稱稱呼佢。<br />\n<br />\n佢為我地犧牲，我地淨低可以做的，就係回憶佢，佢好比佢係我地的社群中消失，如其默稱，我地應給予佢全稱。"},{"pid":"ac4801d5e0385bb1a34296e4f5a0bfd18afba1af","tid":1241680,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:20:59.000Z","msg":"聯署 推"},{"pid":"c09acce9f66934fa8722ae